      <title>伊拉克小麦丰收，今年无需进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/iraq-sees-adequate-wheat-reserves-no-need-for-imports-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊拉克贸易部长阿瑟尔·达乌德在接受采访时表示，伊拉克今年不打算进口小麦，因为该国的小麦库存足以维持七个月，预计会获得丰收。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/iraq-sees-adequate-wheat-reserves-no-need-for-imports-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 13:17:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
