      <title>2024年中国的复苏将“缓慢而坎坷”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/world-economy-latest-china-s-recovery-will-be-slow-and-bumpy-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国看起来几乎肯定会实现 2023 年约 5% 的增长目标，人们的注意力转向通货紧缩风险、房地产危机和持续存在的信心紧缩是否会破坏今年建立动力的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/world-economy-latest-china-s-recovery-will-be-slow-and-bumpy-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
